I had from the Kennedy Center.

00:01:40.522 --> 00:01:42.980
And I was like, why am I getting
junk mail from the Kennedy

00:01:42.980 --> 00:01:43.100
Center?

00:01:43.100 --> 00:01:44.660
I've never even
seen a show there?

00:01:44.660 --> 00:01:45.530
