generous to recommend me

00:02:10.310 --> 00:02:12.170
for this opportunity.

00:02:12.170 --> 00:02:13.910
CAMILLE MASSEY: And
so you've been there

00:02:13.910 --> 00:02:15.620
at the Kennedy Center,
and then you're

00:02:15.620 --> 00:02:19.700
